text: Kupayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Rasmekeyevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 140 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Kushnarenkovo, 4 km from Baytally. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kupayevo
